title: NM Shorts:  Bjarne Melgaard's Cryptoverse
itunes:author: New Models
itunes:summary:
Norwegian artist BJARNE MELGAARD speaks to New Models about his foray into the cryptoverse with his first NFT project, Lightbulb Man — which, in true Melgaard-form, touches the limits of trust in a so-called trustless system.

For more: https://lightbulbman.com/
